RAMDISK:

create /dev/shm/minecraft, set owner to uncovery
copy /home/minecraft/server/worlds/save to /dev/shm/minecraft
create cron job: */10 * * * * rsync -a /dev/shm/minecraft /home/minecraft/server/worlds/save

XMPP Server 
install EPEL repo
install prosody http://prosody.im/doc/configure#adding_a_host
create user server@spiesshofer.com
create user oliver@spiesshofer.com

In-game setup: 
make the time stop in the darklands: /gamerule doDayNightCycle false (http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Commands#gamerule)